<para><ulink url="faqhardwarerelated.html#AEN698">Can Mondo handle
CD-RW?</ulink></para></term>
<varlistentry><term>Q:
<para><ulink url="faqhardwarerelated.html#AEN703">Does Mondo
support tape drives?</ulink></para></term>
<varlistentry><term>Q:
<para><ulink url="faqhardwarerelated.html#AEN708">Does Mondo
support my tape drive??</ulink></para></term>
<varlistentry><term>Q:
<para><ulink url="faqhardwarerelated.html#AEN713">How do I copy the
floppy images from the CD to floppy disks?</ulink></para></term>
<varlistentry><term>Q:
<para><ulink url="faqhardwarerelated.html#AEN722">Sometimes, my
laptop won't mount Mondo CD properly, or something.
Umm...</ulink></para></term>
<varlistentry><term>Q:
<para><ulink url="faqhardwarerelated.html#AEN727">Does Mondo
support RAID?</ulink></para></term>
<varlistentry><term>Q:
<para><ulink url="faqhardwarerelated.html#AEN732">Where is my CD
